description: This file is the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports necessary modules, including React and ReactDOM, as well as CSS styling and the main App component. It initializes the React component tree by attaching it to an HTML element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components inside the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
